title: For Sale:  TacTek CAR-lite Carbine
postcontent: This is a TacTek original. The TacTek CAR-lite is an ultra light AR-15 rifle loaded with features. We start with a Mag Tactical upper and lower. The internal parts are Mag Tactical nickel teflon. The trigger pull is enhanced with a JP enterprises JP Reduced Weight spring kit. Combined with the nickel teflon trigger, disconnector and hammer, this makes for a smooth, crisp trigger break. The barrel is a Daniel Defense 14.5 inch light contour 1 in 7 inch rate-of-twist chrome-lined barrel with a Cavalry arms Cav comp pinned and welded to BATFE specs giving the barrel an overall length of 16 inches. The barrel is torqued to spec using a Core 15 Stressproof barrel nut. The gas system includes a Spike's Tactical Melonited Carbine-length gas tube mated with a Brownell's low-profile gas block. The Bolt Carrier Group is a WMD NIB-X nickel boron plated as is the charging handle. The fore end is a Samson Evolution keymod free-float tube 12.5 inches in length. In order to obtain maximum recoil mitigation, we finish the rifle off with a Mako G-shock recoil-reducing collapsible stock on a Brownell's commercial receiver extension tube. The float tube is topped with Magpul MBUS flip-up sights. All together, the CAR-lite is approximately five pounds. Simply put, this is a light-weight and handy little rifle you have to shoulder to appreciate. Note that this is our demo. If you chose to purchase this model, we will build it from scratch. The approximate wait time is three weeks from start to delivery.
